  "text": "%TFD can give us information about how much attention is given to a particular area of the image (for a review, see [CITATION_1] ), but several studies highlighted the importance of the dimension of an area when dealing with attention deployment (for a review, see [CITATION_2] ). With this formula, we can obtain a nondimensional index suitable for the comparison of AOIs different in size.",
